{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_020.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hm? Are these all the stall applications?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x21b,
            "name_id": 0x32,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes, Master. All is going as well as we could hope."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, they've certainly increased, just as I had planned."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I don't mean to praise my own success, but it's certainly proof of my innovative spirit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hmm?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh jeez, I've been so busy with all the preparations! Huh? Oh, well if it isn't Ayesha...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x57,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "As you can see, I'm rushing around like there's no tomorrow with all these preparations. My goodness."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm. Is something about to start?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's a good thing you asked. We're in the process of preparing the bazaar!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Bazaar? Never heard of it...<CR>It sounds bizarre."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x58,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's like a flea market that's held every month. And to be quite frank with you, it was my idea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Every month, for a few days, we open a market where anyone is welcome to sell their goods."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Various items are gathered from all four cardinal points."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "There'll be sellers from distant places that you've probably never been to, with participation continuing to grow."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It has certainly reached great prosperity and popularity. It's a victory for my planning ability!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that sounds fun...!<CR>It's almost like a festival!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "That's right, it certainly is a festival. I flatter myself with my own overflowing business talent!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "The bazaar starts on the tenth day of every month. By all means, drop by."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "You may even encounter some unexpected lucky finds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'd love to join in!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "In Vierzeberg, a market called a bazaar will periodically be hosted."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Various people will open shops in the bazaar. Some shops will only be open at this time. You may find rare items."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "The bazaar will be held every month from days 10 to 19. It'll be good to reside in Vierzeberg during this period."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Your friends may open shops. This could be a good opportunity to further deepen your friendships."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now use shortcuts.<CR>Press <IM19> to choose where to go and you will be teleported there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can use the shortcut feature to get back to the world map."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "If traveling between areas doesn't consume time, you can use shortcuts."
        }
    ]
}